name: Mnemosyne in the Spiral of Time
description: Goddess of memory, daughter of Uranus and Gaia. Mother of the 9 art-related muses. Analog collage (with digital retouches), combining symbols that relate the act of remembering to different temporalities. Seahorse, snail and half clock. "History of the future", in the lower corner, is a book by Antônio Vieira, from 1718
